{"text_id":27385,"tokens":["As"," light"," field"," images"," continue"," to"," increase"," in"," use"," and"," application",","," it"," becomes"," necessary"," to"," adapt"," existing"," image"," processing"," methods"," to"," this"," unique"," form"," of"," photography","."," In"," this"," paper"," we"," present"," a"," novel"," method"," for"," light"," field"," image"," processing","."," Our"," method"," is"," based"," on"," the"," theory"," of"," wave","front"," reconstruction"," and"," uses"," a"," deep"," learning"," network"," to"," predict"," the"," wave","front"," from"," a"," light"," field"," image","."," We"," then"," apply"," a"," non","-","parametric"," optimization"," algorithm"," to"," minimize"," the"," error"," between"," the"," predicted"," and"," actual"," wave","fron","ts",","," resulting"," in"," an"," image"," with"," improved"," depth"," of"," field"," and"," reduced"," artifacts","."," We"," demonstrate"," the"," effectiveness"," of"," our"," approach"," on"," a"," variety"," of"," light"," field"," images"," and"," show"," that"," it"," out","performs"," existing"," methods","."," Our"," method"," has"," several"," advantages"," over"," existing"," methods","."," First",","," it"," does"," not"," require"," manual"," intervention"," and"," can"," be"," used"," on"," a"," variety"," of"," light"," field"," images","."," Second",","," our"," method"," is"," able"," to"," address"," complex"," artifacts",","," such"," as"," those"," caused"," by"," shallow"," depth"," of"," field"," or"," lens"," aberrations","."," Third",","," the"," method"," is"," computationally"," efficient",","," since"," the"," deep"," learning"," component"," only"," needs"," to"," be"," trained"," once"," and"," then"," applied"," to"," any"," light"," field"," image","."," Finally",","," our"," method"," offers"," a"," degree"," of"," control"," over"," the"," output"," image",","," allowing"," the"," user"," to"," adjust"," parameters"," such"," as"," the"," amount"," of"," blur"," and"," sharpness","."," Overall",","," our"," light"," field"," image"," processing"," method"," provides"," a"," powerful"," and"," versatile"," tool"," for"," improving"," the"," quality"," of"," light"," field"," photographs","."," Our"," results"," suggest"," that"," this"," approach"," can"," be"," used"," to"," reduce"," artifacts",","," improve"," depth"," of"," field",","," and"," produce"," higher"," quality"," images","."],"sub_source":"sci_gen","model":"text-davinci-003","label":1}